## Limitations

The data on veteran homelessness is challenging to obtain and may not fully capture the scope of the issue due to underreporting and the transient nature of the homeless population. Additionally, while the sources used provide a broad overview, they may not reflect the most current statistics or account for regional variations in veteran homelessness. Further research and updated data are necessary for a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.